PostGIS 2.1.6
2015/03/20

 * Enhancements *

  - #3000, Ensure edge splitting and healing algorithms use indexes
  - #3048, Speed up geometry simplification (J.Santana @ CartoDB)
  - #3050, Speed up geometry type reading (J.Santana @ CartoDB)

